        <h2 class="title"><a href="/seti-and-ai">SETI and AI</a></h2>    <span class="submitted">Submitted by <a href="/user/brad" title="View user profile." rel="nofollow">brad</a> on Tue, 2007-10-23 18:02.</span>
    <span class="taxonomy"><ul class="links inline"><li class="first last taxonomy_term_3"><a href="/archives/cat_futurism.html" rel="tag" title="" class="taxonomy_term_3 active">Futurism</a></li>
</ul></span>
    <div class="content"><p>The SETI institute  has a podcast called &#8220;Are we alone?&#8221;</p>

<p>I was interviewed for it at the Singularity Summit, this can be found in their <a href="http://radio.seti.org/past-shows.php#2007-09-24">when machines rule</a> episode.  If you just want to hear me, I start at 32:50 after a long intro explaining the Fermi paradox.</p>
</div>
    <div class="links">&raquo; <ul class="links inline"><li class="first blog_usernames_blog"><a href="/blog/brad" title="Read brad&#039;s latest blog entries." class="blog_usernames_blog">brad&#039;s blog</a></li>
